<div
  style="
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    padding: 30px;
    background: #ffffff;
    color: #111111;
  "
>
  <h2 style="margin-bottom: 25px;">
    Dear {{guest_name}},
  </h2>

  <p>
    It is a pleasure to greet you.
  </p>

  <p>
    Through this message, we are pleased to confirm your attendance
    at our wedding celebration, which will take place on
    <strong>{{wedding_date}}</strong>
    at
    <strong>{{wedding_hour}}</strong>
    in
    <strong>{{wedding_location}}</strong>.
  </p>

  <p>
    Your attendance has been successfully registered with the
    following information:
  </p>

  <ul>
    <li>
      <strong>Name:</strong>
      {{guest_name}}
    </li>

    <li>
      <strong>Email:</strong>
      {{guest_email}}
    </li>

    <li>
      <strong>Phone:</strong>
      {{guest_phone}}
    </li>

    <li>
      <strong>Attendance:</strong>
      {{attendance}}
    </li>
  </ul>

  <p>
    We truly appreciate your confirmation and look forward to sharing
    this unforgettable moment with you.
  </p>

  <p>
    Thank you for being part of our special day.
  </p>

  <br />

  <p>
    Warm regards,
  </p>

  <p>
    <strong>{{hosts}}</strong>
  </p>
</div>